ok charge of the business in  under his leadership the turnover of the bajaj auto the flagship company has gone up from inr million to inr  billion its product portfolio has expanded and the brand has found a global market he is one of indiaâ€™s most distinguished business leaders bike manufacturer india and internationally respected for his business acumen and entrepreneurial spirit    bajaj news    pulsar  becomes the most awarded bike ever watch our md mr rajiv bajaj discuss the importance of yoga on account of international yoga day click to watch pulsar sponsors motorcycle stunt riding team ghost ryderz discover  makes new record  over  lakh bikes sold in just  months bajaj auto gets chinese patent for exhaustec technology bajaj auto launches much awaited kawasaki ninja r − best cc motorcycle in the world a quarter of records for bajaj auto − highest ever turnover of  crore highest ever exports of  vehicles and highest ever net profit of  crore   sitemap       disclaimer       contact us       demerger news       media centre       bhil       bfsl       market tracker copyright  all rights reserved by bajaj auto ltd      bajaj motors  company profile  manufacturer of precision engine components for two wheelers four wheelers tractors heavy machinery     homefacilitiesbajaj groupmilestonecustomerproducts        company profile  management team   structure      contact us                  product enquiry     bajaj motors limited located on the delhijaipur highway on  milestone bajaj motors limited is iso  certified  recommended for ts iso certifications from tuv gmbh germany since its inception in  bajaj motors has its specialization in machining for auto components specifically precision engine components                         units    machining unit   located on the delhijaipur highway on   milestone bajaj motors limited is certified from tuv gmbh germany since its inception in  bajaj motors has its specialization in machining of auto components specifically 