ltd into three corporate entities—bajaj finserv ltd bfl bajaj auto ltd bal and bajaj holdings and investment ltd bhil—was completed with the shares listing on  may  listing and shareholdingedit listingedit bajaj autos equity shares are listed on bombay stock exchange where it is a constituent of the bse sensex index and the national stock exchange of india where it is a constituent of the cnx nifty shareholdingedit on  sep   of the equity shares of the company were owned by the promoters bajaj group and the remaining were owned by others shareholders as on sep shareholding  promoterspriya group  mutual funds fis and insurance companies  foreign institutional investors  individual shareholders  bodies corporate  foreign portfolio investments corporation  gdrs  others  total   employeesedit bajaj auto had a total of  employees as of  march  of which  were women  and  were differentlyabled  it spent ₹ billion us million on employee benefit expenses during the fy – the company is headed by rahul bajaj whose net worth was around us billion in march  awards and recognitionsedit bajaj pulsar  ls received bike of the year  award from bbc  topgear and bike india pulsar  dtsfi received the bike of the year  award by all major indian automobile magazines like overdrive autocar business standard motoring and bike top gear in  bajaj auto won the frost  sullivan super platinum award for manufacturing excellence in its chakan plant it received award for the most customer responsive company in automobiles category in a survey conducted by economic times for the years   and  bajaj auto received the bike maker of the year award in icici bank overdrive awards  bajaj pulsar  dtsi won the bbc world wheels viewers choice two wheeler of the year  award see alsoedit list of motorcycle manufacturers list of scooter manufacturers companies portal referencesedit  a b bajaj auto quarterly results retrieved  july    archived copy pdf archived from the original pdf on  april  retrieved    compan