interest with bal retaining  of the shares it was agreed that bajaj tempo would gradually phase out the use of the tempo brand name as it still belonged to mercedesbenz the name of the company was changed to force motors in may  dropping bajaj as well as tempo over the objections of bajaj auto with whom the company shares a long history as well as a compound wall ktm power sports agedit in november  bajaj auto acquired  stake in ktm power sports ag holding company of ktm sportmotorcycles ag the two companies have signed a cooperation deal by which ktm will provide the knowhow for joint development of the watercooled fourstroke  and  cc engines and bajaj will take over the distribution of ktm products in india and some other southeast asian nations as on  march  bajaj auto held  stake in the company bajajkawasaki end tieup in april edit bajaj and kawasaki have ended their year alliance in india following deepening of ties between the latter and its austrian partner ktm bajaj auto had an alliance with kawasaki for the sale and after sales service of kawasaki motorcycles through its probiking a premium bike dealership network since  these probiking dealerships were later converted to ktm dealerships bajaj auto ltd made a technical assistance agreement with kawasaki japan in  and since then it had cooperated to expand production and sales of motorcycles in india demerger in edit the demerger of bajaj auto ltd into three corporate entities—bajaj finserv ltd bfl bajaj auto ltd bal and bajaj holdings and investment ltd bhil—was completed with the shares listing on  may  listing and shareholdingedit listingedit bajaj autos equity shares are listed on bombay stock exchange where it is a constituent of the bse sensex index and the national stock exchange of india where it is a constituent of the cnx nifty shareholdingedit on  sep   of the equity shares of the company were owned by the promoters bajaj group and the remaining were owned by others shareholders as on sep shareholding  promoterspriya group  mutual funds fis and insurance companies  foreign institutional investors  individual shareholders  bodies corporate  foreign portfolio investments corporation  gdrs  others  total   employeesedit bajaj auto had a total of  employees as of  march  of which  were women  and  were differentlyabled  it spent ₹ billion us million on employee benefit expenses during the fy – the company is headed by rahul bajaj whose net worth was around us billion in march  awards and recognitionsedit bajaj pulsar  ls received bike of the year  award from bbc  topgear and bike india pulsar  dtsfi received the bike of the year  award by all major indian automobile magazines like overdrive autocar business standard motoring and bike top gear in  bajaj auto won the frost  sullivan super platinum award for manufacturing excellence in its chakan plant it received award for the most customer responsive company in automobiles category in a survey conducted by economic times for the years   and  bajaj auto received the bike maker of the year award in icici bank overdrive awards  bajaj pulsar  dtsi won the bbc world wheels viewers choice two wheeler of the year  award see alsoedit list of motorcycle manufacturers list of scooter manufacturers companies portal referencesedit  a b bajaj auto quarterly results retrieved  july    archived copy pdf archived from the original pdf on  april  retrieved    company profile  bajaj auto equitylion retrieved  june    a b bajaj auto at forbes forbes  may  retrieved  october    news article reuters  may  retrieved  may    india is the largest threewheeler industry globally deccan chronicle  march  retrieved  december  the topthree players such as market leader bajaj auto second largest manufacturer piaggio and mahindra and mahindra …   table  top  companies by market capitalisation as on march   nse india  march  retrieved  october    a b c achievements  bajaj auto archived from the original on  october  retrieved  october    a b c 